comments.author: OgNasty
comments.body: Sure, if you can find a buyer for your service I'm sure nobody would have a problem with you offering it here.  You do have a lack of feedback with the exception of one negative so you might have problems receiving payments without an escrow agent.  There's also the rise of AI being taken advantage of to create things like this so you have plenty of competition there as well.  Good luck!
